These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, spinach, tomato, asparagus
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, canadian, australian, argentine
1. the canadian is on the left of the polish##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is the argentine##1
3. the australian is on the right of the polish##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | asparagus | tomato | spinach | cauliflower   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | polish     | australian   | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, traveling, hiking, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse, sailing, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | hiking | dancing | traveling | singing    |
| Sport   | sailing    | lacrosse      | cycling | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, woodworking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, epic, thriller
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | card-games | sudoku | woodworking   | video-games |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | epic | thriller | martial-arts         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts, time-travel, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, lacrosse, golf
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | martial-arts | horror  | time-travel      |
| Sport         | water-polo | golf   | lacrosse | skateboarding |

