.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, carrot, peach, strawberry
4 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, bird, chinchilla
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | strawberry | peach | carrot | pumpkin |
| Pet    | goat       | chinchilla | bird | turtle     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, japanese, spanish, colombian
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, turtle, rat
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish | indonesian | japanese |
| Pet           | dog      | turtle | rat | horse    |

