.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, country, soul, folk
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, pony, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
3. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
5. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | soul | country | rock | folk  |
| Pet           | pony | cat | guinea-pig       | dog |

