.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, electrician, bartender
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, bus, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person driving the ship is the bartender##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the freelancer##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | electrician | freelancer      | lawyer | bartender |
| Transport   | boat          | subway | bus     | ship    |

