.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, western, crime
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, skateboard, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | western       | satire | crime   |
| Transport     | roller | skateboard | bus   | quad-bike |

