2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | 7up | lemonade  | mirinda | soy-milk |
| Transport   | ship | trike | roller          | snowmobile    |

