.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, 7up, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, salsa, soul, metal
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | mirinda  | iced-tea | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul | metal           | salsa   |

