.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, almond-milk, iced-tea
4 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, goldfish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | cola  | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   |
| Pet        | goldfish | dog | hedgehog    | ferret |

