1. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the car##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | scientific | spy | romance |
| Transport     | helicopter | jet-ski    | ship  | car |

