2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | magic-tricks | reading | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | western    | adventure      | time-travel   |

