.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, spanish, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, skateboard, van
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the indian##1
3. the chinese is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the indian is the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish | egyptian | indian   |
| Transport     | skateboard  | helicopter    | taxi       | van |

 